      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of atmospheric performance. This S54B32 power unit features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, this chassis is superlative: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearing service is documented and complete. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with no bushing deflection or damper fatigue. Every fluid circuit has been flushed, and the engine exhibits nominal compression values across all six cylinders. This is a turn-key, purist-spec machine with zero deferred maintenance, preserved in showroom condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
